posting_body: ['Welcome to Chorus', "Chorus is prominently and conveniently located at the cross point of SF's most dynamic neighborhoods.", 'The private residences are complete with the latest technology and top-of-the-line appliances.', 'Outside the home, Chorus residents enjoy access to a unique collection of amenities including a rooftop pool, outdoor American Ninja Warrior course, solarium, speakeasy and lobby cocktail bar.', 'The community is expertly maintained 24 hours a day by a dedicated team with attention to every detail.', 'Join the Chorus family today!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Bike Storage & Repair', 'BBQ/Picnic Area', 'Backyard terrace with pizza oven', 'Rooftop Deck', 'Electric Car Charging Stations', 'Skybox lounge', 'Indoor/outdoor fitness lab with functional training equipment and 10 rotating classes per week', 'Keyless Entry', 'Saltwater pool with private cabanas, lounge areas and Jacuzzi', 'Co-working space with private conference rooms', 'Dog run, grooming station and pet wash', 'In-Unit Laundry', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
